## Attribution Examples

### HTML Footer Example
```html
<footer>
  <p>
    Portfolio design by 
    <a href="https://github.com/kaancivelek" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      Kaan Civelek
    </a>
  </p>
</footer>
```

### React Component Example
```jsx
<footer style={{ textAlign: 'center', padding: '1rem', fontSize: '0.875rem' }}>
  Portfolio template by{' '}
  <a 
    href="https://github.com/kaancivelek/kaancivelek-portfolio"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
  >
    Kaan Civelek
  </a>
</footer>
```

